text: Hunter James Schafer (born December 31, 1998) is an American fashion model, actor, and LGBTQ rights activist. In 2019, she played transgender high school student Jules Vaughn in the HBO series Euphoria. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:American LGBT rights activists Category:American movie actors Category:LGBT models Category:LGBT actors Category:Transgender women Category:Models from New Jersey Category:Models from North Carolina Category:LGBT people from New Jersey Category:Actors from Trenton, New Jersey Category:Actors from North Carolina
